learning_outcomes.en:
The student knows
- the principles of assessment of children's development;
- how to collect the information about psychological development of children in different ages;
- how to prepare the investigation plan for children with different ages;
- how to draft the report based on the child's investigation;
- what services are needed for rehabilitation depending on the type of special need.
The student analyses:
- their readiness and areas of development to work as a special education teacher or speech therapist, plans their future studies based on their need of development.

learning_outcomes.et:
Ainekursuse läbinud üliõpilane 
- tunneb laste arengutaseme hindamise põhimõtteid;
- on kursis erivajaduste märkamist ja identifitseerimist puudutava seadusandlusega;
- omab ülevaadet arengu eri valdkondade uurimise võimalustest eri vanuses lastel;
- omab ülevaadet erivajaduste identifitseerimise protsessist ja erinevate spetsialistide rollist selles;
- teab, millised teenused on vajalikud erivajadustega laste rehabiliteerimiseks sõltuvalt erivajaduse tüübist.
- analüüsib iseenda pädevust ja arenguvajadusi eripedagoogina/logopeedina töötamiseks, planeerib oma edasisi õpinguid sellele tuginedes.
